<subSubSection id="A0FF676610490F9CBA9C194EF6C717F8" pageId="7" pageNumber="86" type="dispersal potential">
<paragraph id="78FDED5F6C523E07ABC18927D27DAA6C" pageId="7" pageNumber="86">Dispersal potential.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="204847CADAC92BAEE326594116B2E64F" pageId="7" pageNumber="86">These beetles are macropterous and capable of flight. They are moderately swift and agile runners.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E6494A457002E46D9EBD5AEA20F81086" pageId="7" pageNumber="86" type="way of life">
<paragraph id="E0390F236AF7403217E4D19A99E4F4F9" pageId="7" pageNumber="86">Way of life.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0AF456B4D96862916915AA9900A51B2B" pageId="7" pageNumber="86">The adult holotype was collected in a flight intercept trap in the rainforest understory. The adult holotype was active in November, at the end of the dry season.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
